<html>
    <head>
        <style>
            body {
                background-color: #f2f2f2;
                font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
                font-size: 16px;
                color: #333;
            }

            p {
				font-size: 24px;
                color: #555;
                margin: 10px 0;
				text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 2px;
            }

            h3 {
                font-size: 24px;
                color: #555;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 2px;
            }

            .message {
                background-color: #fff;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
                padding: 30px;
                border-radius: 10px;
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
                line-height: 1.5;
            }

            .reset-button {
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 18px;
                font-weight: bold;
                text-align: center;
                text-decoration: none;
                background-color: #007bff;
                color: #fff;
                border-radius: 5px;
                transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            }

            .reset-button:hover {
                background-color: #0056b3;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="message">
            <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
            <h3>(如果您从未请求发送重置密码，请忽略此邮件)</h3>
            <a href="{{link}}" class="reset-button">重置密码</a>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
